{"tid":2014842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係接freelance，呢3個月搵4000$，過唔到生活","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T13:09:06.000Z","uid":36788,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c8c7c129a6ec2ad06e91a28d3e025c4b86a212","tid":2014842,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"我日日都係係西九龍中心好似阿伯鳩坐，唔敢返屋企"},{"pid":"93b69553b92113acc5700b46e3408cfb62a68d9c","tid":2014842,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔接多幾單 freelance"},{"pid":"017fbbdfbb9e055a9ce9de4cbb749b5ba20229bd","tid":2014842,"uid":5490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"鳩坐都唔送外賣？"},{"pid":"8a253e226038fedec4790d6e240ab2bd6d7ae36f","tid":2014842,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"炒股啦"},{"pid":"98e0208481c66265c19c067c3d998374fd88e5be","tid":2014842,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"考警察啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff68bdce58fb55df2c63d0b4d7a0226aa524ffde","tid":2014842,"uid":256215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"每月4000定3個月4000? 無儲蓄?  <br />\n<br />\n我最近2個月都冇收入，都有時去公園鳩坐。主係嗰種前唔汒汒既空虛感真係好難頂。 一係屋企耐就好唔舒服"},{"pid":"2ed817359602e2f0ee13f3487e18cbe0beabbdd9","tid":2014842,"uid":287015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"係邊行freelance? design?"},{"pid":"f93ab227c734f2a72610daa1712642c355d7fd33","tid":2014842,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7c8c7c129a6ec2ad06e91a28d3e025c4b86a212","tid":2014842,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"我日日都係係西九龍中心好似阿伯鳩坐，唔敢返屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"晏晝食咩？"},{"pid":"e4901f7a7e874c4c218bef962262a375955b4f17","tid":2014842,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"Design ?"},{"pid":"752c770bd41c9df0527a984f626efc84f70984c5","tid":2014842,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"我都收入大跌<br />\n最近睇左好多正能量野<br />\n希望幫到大家<br />\n一定要保持頭腦清醒同正能量<br />\n研究下點樣做網上宣傳，直播<br />\n發輝網絡力量"},{"pid":"600b61ae248784bb07daef9423ccc8afc38c6790","tid":2014842,"uid":26335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:06:18.000Z","msg":"好你少少，我都係冇晒freelance，不過好彩仲有份pt返吊下命仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲讀緊書，以前3個月點都接到一兩單freelance，平均每單賺四五千(拍片剪片一腳踢)，加埋得閒返下其他pt，每個月輕鬆淨袋1萬，宜家乜freelance都冇晒，pt又cut左一半更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73277f08defbaca96f2ad50027f9f6a9dbd876e0","tid":2014842,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n驚比屋企人知失業"},{"pid":"618c685fec751751a81b1e0365a64ca989fa917b","tid":2014842,"uid":240533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"山不轉路轉，路不轉人轉。<br />\n你要自己幫自己，如果日日返去都係坐既話，咁就要諗下計點過呢關。做住Deliveroo 步兵都要頂住先。有個別問題而做唔到步兵，都可以多做嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n有危先有機，係日常既時候，正常黎講都發唔到圍，一早比大企業霸哂d機會。所以轉個角度黎睇，呢次可以係一次機會。"},{"pid":"5f231d2630181d399846573f40e0c3679dab81cf","tid":2014842,"uid":104833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"搵返份牛工打住先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d15751971cabeaf7f68130736d0d4cf68c58542","tid":2014842,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"我有正職都做緊freelance<br />\n呢幾個月freelance收入都係每月$3-4000左右<br />\n巴打做邊行？"},{"pid":"ee413abd33bff2340c3faa3769a7f2b29aa828b3","tid":2014842,"uid":36788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93b69553b92113acc5700b46e3408cfb62a68d9c","tid":2014842,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔接多幾單 freelance"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"有生意先得架"},{"pid":"a16bac89802612f6ac7962e50dfa48def3254bb2","tid":2014842,"uid":36788,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"017fbbdfbb9e055a9ce9de4cbb749b5ba20229bd","tid":2014842,"uid":5490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"鳩坐都唔送外賣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"唔肯低頭囉"},{"pid":"9f61ce6bcad2501ce4f11d257e760ba6b5c39146","tid":2014842,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16bac89802612f6ac7962e50dfa48def3254bb2","tid":2014842,"uid":36788,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"017fbbdfbb9e055a9ce9de4cbb749b5ba20229bd","tid":2014842,"uid":5490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"鳩坐都唔送外賣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"唔肯低頭囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"又唔係長做，大把人近排無聊送外賣，見到好多學生做"},{"pid":"ebb76922529e7933f28f7434b8251ca18531cb0d","tid":2014842,"uid":148981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"冇技能可以做咩freelance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25c7d60ce666df5b2235c6a0714959a0dc2b617","tid":2014842,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"我都最近少咗job，啲人仲成日以為我哋freelance做嘢唔受影響<br />\n唯有襯呢排得閒，update晒啲幾年冇郁過嘅Linkedin、CV、cover letter，準備隨時ready再出擊<br />\n<br />\n本來成日嫌忙想多啲私人時間，但一停手就驚冇嘢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窮人命"}]}